      <article id="summary">
        <h4 class="section-heading">Summary</h4>
        <div class="summary">
          <p>Set in 1960s New York, the sexy, stylized and provocative AMC drama <em>Mad Men</em> follows the lives of the ruthlessly competitive men and women of Madison Avenue advertising, an ego-driven world where key players make an art of the sell.</p>
        </div>
